snippet.title: KickBeat Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
KickBeat is an award-winning music title with a hard hitting soundtrack offering players several innovative ways to interact with music. Beat-matching mechanics come to life in this kung-fu style music fighter, featuring licensed tracks from a diverse lineup of artists from well known bands such as Pendulum and Marilyn Manson, to indie pioneers Celldweller and Blue Stahli, to hidden talents like electronic music producer Voicians and Taiwanese rapper Shen Yi. 

KickBeat is available on PC and consoles.

http://kickbeat.com/
